0.  READ-ITEM ARR N
1.  COMPARE N TO ZERO
2.  IF EQUAL GOTO 20
3.  STORE ZERO IN SWAPPED
4.  STORE ZERO IN START
5.  SUBTRACT ONE FROM N STORE IN END
6.  STORE ZERO IN SWAPPED
7.  STORE START IN I
8.  COMPARE I TO END
9.  IF EQUAL GOTO 14
10. READ ARR(I) INTO REGA
11. READ ARR(I+1) INTO REGB
12. COMPARE REGA TO REGB
13. IF GREATER GOTO SWAP-FWD
13A. ADD ONE TO I GOTO 8
SWAP-FWD. STORE REGB IN ARR(I)
           STORE REGA IN ARR(I+1)
           STORE ONE IN SWAPPED
           ADD ONE TO I
           GOTO 8
14. COMPARE SWAPPED TO ZERO
15. IF EQUAL GOTO 20
16. STORE ZERO IN SWAPPED
17. SUBTRACT ONE FROM END
18. STORE END IN I SUBTRACT ONE FROM I
19. COMPARE I TO START
19A. IF LESS GOTO INCREMENT
     READ ARR(I) INTO REGA
     READ ARR(I+1) INTO REGB
     COMPARE REGA TO REGB
     IF GREATER GOTO SWAP-BWD
     SUBTRACT ONE FROM I GOTO 19
SWAP-BWD. STORE REGB IN ARR(I)
           STORE REGA IN ARR(I+1)
           STORE ONE IN SWAPPED
           SUBTRACT ONE FROM I GOTO 19
INCREMENT. ADD ONE TO START GOTO 6
20. STOP
